    "A specific implementation of GAN that revealed itself as relevant in the literature is Large Scale Adversarial Representation Learning (BigBiGAN) (Donahue and Simonyan 2019).",
    "BigBiGAN is a method for image generation and representation learning.",
    "This method allows for the extraction of features in an unsupervised way from a GAN and scales up the previously existing algorithms leading to an improved GAN model.",
